# DRL Stock Trading System - Git Ignore Rules

# ========== Data Files ==========
*.csv
*.pkl
*.pth
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.npy
*.npz

# ========== Experiment Results ==========
# Keep experiment directories but ignore large binary files inside them
*experiment*/models/*.pth
*experiment*/checkpoints/*.pth
*_experiment/models/*.pth
*_experiment/checkpoints/*.pth

